commentTextItems.html: lifts over the fielders, the ball runs away to the cover boundary, cheers all round

commentPostTextItems.html: Well Scotland have chased down Ireland's massive total of 320, with 9 balls and 5 wickets to spare. It has been a great match and the wicket was good, but for two scores of 300+ they were firing on all cylinders. They were even the whole way through until Berrington fired 50 off 20 balls to vault Scotland ahead. Do join us tomorrow for Scotland v Sri-Lanka, but for now from Callum Stewart, have a good evening.

milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (643) involving teams Ireland & Scotland in ODIs
Berrington has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (6) in ODIs for SCOT, going past Paul Hoffmann's 4
Fraser Watts has scored 10 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for SCOT breaking Hamilton's record
